>First of all, congratulations on your engagement!</h2>\r\nYour wedding day is one of the most important days of your life.  We will make your event fun &amp; something your guests will remember for years!\r\n\r\nLive Bands, Solo/Duet musicians, Hula, Fire-dancers, &amp; Theme Parties are all options. We also do Indian, Jewish, Latin or other multi-cultural weddings.\r\n\r\nLA Beats DJs  has you covered for any event, with over 18 years of experience!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_style=\"solid\" disabled=\"off\"]\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Ceremony Package</h2>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_style=\"solid\" disabled=\"off\"]\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Mobile Sound System</li>\r\n 	<li>1 Professional wireless lapel microphone</li>\r\n 	<li>1 Wireless handheld microphone</li>\r\n 	<li>Customized ceremony music playlist</li>\r\n 	<li>Music coordination during ceremony</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_style=\"solid\" disabled=\"off\"]\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Reception Package</h2>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_style=\"solid\" disabled=\"off\"]\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Set up one hour prior to event start time</li>\r\n 	<li>DJ &amp; MC services by skilled professional</li>\r\n 	<li>Unlimited consultations &amp; advice (phone, meetup, emails)</li>\r\n 	<li>Customized playlist, 100% what you want to hear!</li>\r\n 	<li>Wireless handheld microphone for speeches &amp; toasts.</li>\r\n 	<li>Complim