px|40px|50px\" disabled=\"off\"]\r\n\r\nLet’s bring your team together &amp; have some FUN in Los Angeles!\r\n\r\nLA Beats DJs offers special packages designed to fit your specific event needs and budget.  Big corporate party in a huge ballroom, or smaller party with your team…we got you!\r\n\r\nWe specialize in DJ’s but can offer ALL entertainment for your Los Angeles event.\r\n\r\nLive Bands, Solo/Duet musicians, Fire-dancers, Theme Parties &amp; more!\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_style=\"solid\" disabled=\"off\"]\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Company Events</h2>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_style=\"solid\" disabled=\"off\"]\r\n\r\nLA Beats DJs provides professional DJ, MC, Soundsystem &amp; Lighting services for your Company Events!   From holiday parties to promotional events, LA Beats DJs can help you curate and coordinate a fabulous night of music &amp; dance!\r\n\r\nWe have performed at most major venues all over LA including Four Seasons, Ritz-Carlton &amp; more!\r\n\r\nFormer clients such as Beats Audio, Intel, HP, Golden Gates National Parks Conservancy, Hawaii Yoga Festival, 2014 Maroon 5 after-party to name a few.\r\n\r\nLA Beats DJs has 18 years of experience rocking crowds! You can rest assured that our DJs will provide exactly the music you want, with style &amp; finesse.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_style=\"solid\" disabled=\"off\"]\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>LA Beats DJs take pride in our professional approach.  From making ourselves accessible to the client for every aspect of event planning (email, phone, or in person), to using the highest quality equipment, we make sure that the client always feels confident that their event will be a success.  We specialize in DJ’s but have other options of entertainment for your event as well.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Live Music</li>\r\n 	<li>Bands</li>\r\n 	<li>Fire dancers</li>\r\n 	<li>Theme Parties</li>\r\n 	<li>Uplighting, Fog Machines &amp; other party toys!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" global_module=\"4105\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"off\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" module_id=\"contact\"][et_pb_row global_parent=\"4105\" admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" padding_left_2=\"50px\" column_padding_mobile=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_image global_parent=\"4105\" admin_label=\"LA beats Djs logo\" src=\"http://labeatsdjs.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/music-logo2.png\" alt=\"LA Djs beats logo\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_overlay=\"off\" animation=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"left\" force_fullwidth=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_image][et_pb_text global_parent=\"4105\" admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n<p><script src=\"//www.weddingwire.c