edding DJ for making our night memorable!”</em></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bethany & Kyle  5/6/2016</span></p>[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide background_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0)\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“LA Beats DJs was such a pleasure to deal with and was really accommodating with our song choices and set up. They always got back to me quickly if I had any questions. I found LABeatsDjs to be really reliable & easygoing, not to mention their great mixing skills.”</em></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Anna & Dave 8/24/2015</span></p>[/et_pb_slide][/et_pb_slider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" transparent_background=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" fullwidth=\"on\" disabled_on=\"on|on|\" admin_label=\"Section\"][et_pb_fullwidth_slider show_arrows=\"off\" show_pagination=\"off\" parallax=\"on\" remove_inner_shadow=\"on\" disabled_on=\"off|off|off\" admin_label=\"Fullwidth Slider\"][et_pb_slide background_image=\"http://labeatsdjs.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Maui_Wedding_DJ_28_banner1980stripe.png\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\"][/et_pb_slide][/et_pb_fullwidth_slider][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_mobile=\"off\" admin_label=\"Section\" module_id=\"about\"][et_pb_row padding_mobile=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\" admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://labeatsdjs.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Adrian-Round.png\" alt=\"Maui Wedding DJ\" animation=\"off\" max_