ks directly with clients. He has DJ\'d most of the big venues, including The Ritz Carlton, The Hyatt, Westin, etc.  [learn_more]</span></p><p>Proud member of WeddingWire (the nations leading site for wedding vendors), LA Beats DJs Club & LA Wedding Association.  2014 & 2015 Bride’s Choice Award from WeddingWire, placing LA Beats DJs in the Top 5% of Wedding Professionals.</p><p>Whether it’s a wedding, company event, or private party, we will rise to the occasion & ignite your dance floor!</p><p>Adrian has been a DJ since 1997 & his DJ skills, amazing music collection, listening & people skills, plus quality gear makes him the #1 LA Beats DJs!</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">[/learn_more]  </span></p><p>*Most in demand DJs & other wedding vendors book at least 6-9 months in advance, so call now to reserve your precious date!</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_mobile=\"off\" admin_label=\"Section\" module_id=\"contact\" global_module=\"4105\"][et_pb_row padding_mobile=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"off\" padding_left_2=\"50px\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"off\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://labeatsdjs.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/music-logo2.png\" alt=\"LA Djs beats logo\" animation=\"off\" admin_label=\"LA beats Djs logo\"][/et_pb_image][et_pb_text text_orientation=\"center\" admin_label=\"Text\"]\n\n<p><script src=\"//www.weddingwire.com/assets/vendor/widgets/my-reviews-477a27662bf1bc2843763ee1950ed856.js\" type=\"application/javascript\"></script></p><div id=\"ww-widget-reviews\" class=\"ww-reset ww-reviews-widget\"><div class=\"ww-reviews-placeholder\">Read all of our wedding reviews on our<br /> <a href=\"https://www.weddingwire.com/biz/maui-beats-paia/69ba6b2f384df3ca.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Maui