riety of music at their disposal and had everyone (I mean EVERYONE) dancing the night away!”</em></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Crystal & Robert  3/27/2015</span></p>[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide background_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0)\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“LA Beats DJs made the evening 110% about my husband and I. We could not be more grateful and highly recommend them as a DJ for any event! Thank\'s to our LA Wedding DJ for making our night memorable!”</em></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bethany & Kyle  5/6/2016</span></p>[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide background_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0)\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“LA Beats DJs was such a pleasure to deal with and was really accommodating with our song choices and set up. They always got back to me quickly if I had any questions. I found LABeatsDjs to be really reliable & easygoing, not to mention their great mixing skills.”</em></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Anna & Dave 8/24/2015</span></p>[/et_pb_slide][/et_pb_slider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" transparent_background=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" fullwidth=\"on\" disabled_on=\"on|on|\" admin_label=\"Section\"][et_pb_fullwidth_slider show_arrows=\"off\" show_pagination=\"off\" parallax=\"on\" remove_inner_shadow=\"on\" disabled_on=\"off|off|off\" admin_label=\"Fullwidth Slider\"][et_pb_slide background_image=\"http://labeatsdjs.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Maui_Wedding_DJ_28_banner1980stripe.