" src=\"http://labeatsdjs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/CCA17-Final-Badge.png\" alt=\"Wedding Wire Award 2017\" url=\"https://www.weddingwire.com/reviews/maui-beats-paia/69ba6b2f384df3ca.html\" url_new_window=\"on\" animation=\"off\" align=\"center\" max_width=\"200px\" force_fullwidth=\"on\" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Wedding Wire Award 2015\" src=\"http://labeatsdjs.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/200CCA15-Badge.png\" alt=\"Wedding Wire Award 2015\" url=\"https://www.weddingwire.com/reviews/maui-beats-paia/69ba6b2f384df3ca.html\" url_new_window=\"on\" animation=\"off\" align=\"center\" max_width=\"200px\" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Wedding Wire Award 2014\" src=\"http://labeatsdjs.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/200CCA14-Badge.png\" alt=\"Wedding Wire Award 2014\" url=\"https://www.weddingwire.com/reviews/maui-beats-paia/69ba6b2f384df3ca.html\" url_new_window=\"on\" animation=\"off\" align=\"center\" max_width=\"200px\" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://labeatsdjs.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/200WeddingWire-Rated-Blue-Business.png\" alt=\"Wedding Wire Award 2017\" url=\"https://www.weddingwire.com/reviews/la-beats-djs-los-angeles/69ba6b2f384df3ca.html\" url_new_window=\"on\" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" admin_label=\"Section\" background_color=\"#e2e2e2\" custom_padding=\"30px||20px|\" padding_mobile=\"off\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" padding_mobile=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\" parallax_method_1=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"center\" custom_margin=\"||0px|\" custom_padding=\"||0px|\"]\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-4086 aligncenter\" src=\"http://labeatsdjs.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/five-stars.png\" alt=\"five-stars\" width=\"239\" height=\"80\" /></p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_slider admin_label=\"Testimonials\" show_arrows=\"off\" show_pagination=\"off\" auto=\"on\" auto_speed=\"8500\" remove_inner_shadow=\"on\" top_padding=\"20px\" bottom_padding=\"20px\" header_font_size=\"30\" header_line_height=\"1.2em\"]\r\n\r\n[et_pb_slide background_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0)\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“We (and our guests!) loved having LA Beats DJs as our LA Wedding DJ. They had an amazing variety of music at their disposal and had everyone (I mean EVERYONE) dancing the night away!”</em></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Crystal & Robert  3/27/2015</span></p>[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide background_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0)\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“LA Beats DJs made the evening 110% about my husband and I. We could not be more grateful and highly recommend them as a DJ for any event! Thank\'s to our LA Wedding DJ for making our night memorable!”</em></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bethany & Kyle  5/6/2016</span></p>[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide background_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0)\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“LA Beats DJs was such a pleasure to deal with and was really accommodating with our song choices and set up. They always got back to me quickly if I had any questions. I found LABeatsDjs to be really reliable & easygoing, not to mention their great mixing skills.”</em></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Anna & Dave 8/24/2015</span></p>[/et_pb_slide]\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_slider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" admin_label=\"Section\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_mobile=\"off\" module_id=\"about\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" padding_mobile=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://labeatsdjs.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Adrian-Round.png\" alt=\"Maui Wedding DJ\" animation=\"off\" max_width=\"250px\" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\"]\r\n\r\n<h3><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">LA Beats DJs was founded by LA Wedding DJ Adrian Blackhurst, aka DJ Boogiemeister, to bring great music to the masses! </span></em></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He works with various wedding planners & books directly with clients. He has DJ\'d most of the big venues, including The Ritz Carlton, The Hyatt, Westin, etc.  [learn_more]</span></p><p>Proud member of WeddingWire (the nations leading site for wedding vendors), LA Beats DJs Club & LA Wedding Association.  2014 & 2015 Bride’s Choice Award from WeddingWire, placing LA Beats DJs in the Top 5% of Wedding Professionals.</p><p>Whether it’s a wedding, company event, or private party, we will rise to the occasion & ignite your dance floor!</p><p>Adrian has been a DJ since 1997 & his DJ skills, amazing music collection, listening & people skills, plus quality gear makes him the #1 LA Beats DJs!</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">[/learn_more]  </span></p><p>*Most in demand DJs & other wedding vendors book at least 6-9 months in advance, so call now to reserve your precious date!</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" padding_mobile=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://labeatsdjs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/pleasuremaker.png\" alt=\"Maui Wedding DJ\" animation=\"off\" max_width=\"250px\" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\"]\r\n\r\n<p><br/></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h3><em>DJ Pleasuremaker</em></h3>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Pleasuremaker is a party starting ball of energy! When he performs he brings an uplifting and soulful blend of Electro, Organic, Tropical, Disco, Funky, and high energy sounds that keep folks dancing and wanting more.</span>&nbsp;[learn_more]</span>He always delivers large on great times and has audiences wanting more of that pleasure.&nbsp; He has experience with many weddings &amp; company events, always catering to your needs!</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>As a founder of the Afrolicious party &amp; band he has worked alongside amazing artists from around the globe including Thievery Corporation, Nickodemus, Balkan Beat Box,Third World, Femi Kuti, Beats Antique &amp; more. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">[/learn_more]</span></p>\r\n<p><br/></p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"off\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" module_id=\"contact\" global_module=\"4105\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" global_parent=\"4105\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" padding_left_2=\"50px\" column_padding_mobile=\"off\